== Adlem jivit ani fattbhuim[sudar] ==
Guru Dutt hacho zolm 9 Julh 1925, Bangalore-ant zalo. Tachem niz nanv Vasanth Kumar Shivashankar Padukone punn tem Guru Dutt nanvan bodolpant ailem zachem karonn ek bhurgeponnar zalolo obsoeg zavn asa,ani ti ek dharzonneachi nivodd mhonn sotmanpant ieta.[6] Tacho avoi bapui adim Karvar rabito kortalim punn uprant dusre kodden ravpak gelim.Duttan aplem survatechem bhurgeponn  Bhowanipore-ant kaddlem[7]Tachi bhoinni Lalita Lajmi ek famad Bharoti rongovpi zavn asa [8]. Tachi dhuvddi Kalpana Lajmi ek famad Bharoti film digdorspi, nirmovpi ani pott kotha borovpi asli<ref>{{Citation|title=Kalpana Lajmi|date=2018-09-26|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Kalpana_Lajmi&oldid=861284132|work=Wikipedia|language=en|access-date=2018-11-23}}</ref>

== Karkird[sudar] ==

=== Adli karkird[sudar ===
Apnnank telephone operatorachi nokri Lever Brothers karkhanneant Calcutta mell’llea mhonn Duttan ghora tar kelo ki. Punn rokhddench taka tea nokre dhadosponn na mhonn disun ailem ani tannem ti soddli. Uprant to aplea avoibapaichea sangatak Mumboi 1944 vorsa ravunk gelo.

Punn, tachea tivan taka ek nokri melloili ji eka tin vorsanchea kontrad zo  Punnechea Prabhat Film Company kodden  1944 aslo. Ho ek poili film kaddpacho kendr aslo zannem  boreantlo boro fixalkaiecho monis V. Shantaram tankam soddun gelolo pollelem, zannem apli khas prostuti komponi Kala Mandir sador keli.  Prabhat Film Company hanga  Duttachi don monxam kodde bhett zali je tache bore ixtt jivit bhor asle zanchim nanvam kolakar Rehman ani Dev Anand zavn asat.

Dutt-an Sri Krishnachem Chand filmant1944 vorsa ek lhan patr kelem.  1945 vorsa, obhinoi korun tannem  Vishram Bedekar haka digdorxonant Lakhrani  filmant mozot keli , ani 1946 vorsa tannem palvi digdorspi ani nach digdorspi koso  P. L. Santoshichea Hum Ek Hain filmant vavurlo.

Ho kontrad 1947 vorsa somplo, punn Dutt'ache avoin taka ek mukt adhari koso Baburao Pai, Prabhat Film Company and Studiocho CEO sangata vavurpak dhaddlo. Punn, tea uprant, sumar dha mhoineamni, to bekar urlo ani aplea kuttumba sangata Mumboint  Matunga vibhagant ravlo. Hea vellar, Dutt-an Inglix borovpant zannvai zoddli ani The Illustrated Weekly of India, ek thollavi satalleache Inglix nemalleak mottveo kannio borovpak laglo.

=== Nach digdorspi, kolakar ani palvi digdorspi[sudar] ===
Zorui Dutt-ak Prabhat Film Komponen ek nach digdorspi koso bhaddean ghetlolo,punn taka obhinoi korpachi ani palvi digdorspeachem kam dilem.  1947 vorsa, Prabhat-ak opies ietoch, Dutt Mumboi portolo, zoim to tea vellachea famad digdorspeam sangata kam korunk laglo je zavn asle Girls' School filmacho Amiya Chakravarty , ani Bombay Talkiesachea  Sangram filmacho Gyan Mukherjee . Uprant,Dev Anand-an taka kam aplea nove komponent digdorspeachem kam dilem ani te komponechem nanv, Navketan aslem aplem poilea filmank opies ailea uprant.

Duttachem poilem film, Navketanachem Baazi, 1951 vorsa sador zalem.Tem 1940 vorsantea Hollywood filmachea xoilik  zantunt noitik duvarthi nott, kaide moddpi jolpori ani savllechea viz vevosthek argam divpi zavn aslem

Zor  Dutt ek film toiar korit zalear, tannem Dev Anandak mukhel nott koso ghevpacho, ani zor Anand film prostut korit zalear  to Duttak tacho digdorspi kortolo, oxe eke koblaticher, Dev Anand ani Dutt pavlole. Anandan magir Duttacho upeog aplea Baazi filmant kelo, ani Dutt-an Anand-ak  C.I.D-.nt ghetlo.  Duttachea mornna uprant, Anand-an mhollem "To ek tornnatto aslo, tannem khontichim filma korunk favo naslem. "<ref name="anand">{{Cite web|url=http://dearcinema.com/interview/dev-anand-remembers-guru-dutt/1824|title=Interview: Dev Anand Remembers Guru Dutt|publisher=dearcinema.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110404231145/http://dearcinema.com/interview/dev-anand-remembers-guru-dutt/1824|archive-date=4 April 2011}}</ref>

Dutt ani Anand he don chodd lokprio film Baazi, ani Jaal sangatan korpache. Dutt, ani Chetan Anand(Anandacho vhoddlo bhav) zovui ek digdorspi aslo, hanche modem sorjonxil motbhed uprasun  fuddlim prokolpam avghodd kelim.[ul'lekh zai]{{citation needed|date=September 2016}}

=== Digdorspi koso[sudar] ===
<span>Baazi ek iesvont film zalem. Dut-tan uprant Jaal ani Baaz filmani pattlav kelo. Donui filmam bori zodd korunk pavunk nant punn tannim Guru Dutt pongodd sangatak haddlo zannim budvontkai fuddlea filmani dakhoili. Johnny Walker(fokanner), V.K. Murthy (fottografor), ani Abrar Alvi (borovpi-digdorspi), heram modem hancho tannem sod lailo ani tankam xikovp dilem, . Taka Waheeda Rehman-ak Hindi cinemant haddpak xroi divpant ailam. Dutta-n digdorxon ani kam tantunt kelem kiteak taka favo to kolakar mukhel kam korpak mellunk naslo, hem Baazi filman nond kelem. </span>

Dutt-ache fuddlea filmank noxib mevlem, 1954 vorsantlea chodd komavpi Aar Paar film zalem. Hacho pattlav 1955  vorsantlea chodd lokprio Mr. & Mrs. '55, uprant C.I.D., Sailaab ani 1957 vorsa, Pyaasa – ek kovichi kanni, durlokx korpi lokamni nakarloleachi, zaka ies fokot aplea dolleank dispi mornnant favo zata. Duttan hea panch filma modlea tin filmani mukhel nottachem kam kelem. 

Tachem  1959  vorsantleKaagaz Ke Phool ek khor niraxechem aslem. Tannem tea filmant zaitoch mog, duddu ani koxtt ghatlole, zachi kanni eka famad digdorspeachi (Duttan tem patr kelolem) asli zo eka nottiechea mogan (Waheeda Rehmanan patr kelolea,Duttachea khorea mogachi) asli.. Kaagaz Ke Phool duddu komanvk pavunk na ani  Dutt-acher sanvar ailo.Sogllim tachea chitrsallentlim uprantlim filma odhikrutponni her digdorspeamni hatall’llim kiteak aplem nanv duddu mellovpak maldisanv zavn asa mhonn Dutt-ak dislem. 

Dutta-n aplem duddu mellovpi chodd lokprio film Chaudhvin Ka Chand hantunt aplo probhav ghatlo. Ek Musolmanachem mogachem-trikonnichea filmant Guru Dutt-a sangatak Waheeda Rehman ani Rehman hannim bhag ghetlo. Filmachem digdorxon  M. Sadiq hannem kelem tachi suchi "Chaudhvin Ka Chand Ho" eka kherit rongan chitraili,HI ekuch ghoddnni zoim amkam Guru Dutt rongit rupan dista .<ref>[http://boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=166&catName=MTk2MA== Box Office 1960]. BoxOffice India.com {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120922021750/http://boxofficeindia.com/showProd.php?itemCat=166&catName=MTk2MA==|date=22 September 2012}}</ref>

''Sahib Bibi Aur Ghulam, ek nirnnoiak ani veparant iesiesvi film tachea alaxiro ditolea borovpean Abrar Alvi, hannem digdorxit kelem zaka Filmfare acho boreantlo boro digdorspi tosrip favo zalem.Filmant  xokantikechi ranni Meena Kumari ani Guru Dutt Rehman ani Waheeda Rehman soho kolakar koxe asle. Tem film Dutt-anuch digdorxon kelem ho bhas filmachi nottien Waheeda Rehman, hinnem i fakai nakarli.''.<ref>[http://in.rediff.com/movies/2004/oct/11guru.htm "Nobody really knows what happened on October 10"]. In.rediff.com (11 October 2004). Retrieved on 2018-11-14.</ref>

=== Nimanneo prostuteo[sudar] ===
1964  vorsa Dutt Sanjh Aur Savera,  hea aplea nimannea filmant to Meena Kumari sangatak dislo jem Hrishikesh Mukherjee, hannem digdorxit kelelem . Baharen Phir Bhi Aayengi hem tachem nimannem film aslem zantunt to tachea mornnachea vellar kam kortalo. Tacho mukhel patracho  zago Dharmendran ghetlo ani tem film1966 vorsa tea pongddagchem nimannem film aslem.

== Moronn[sudar] ==
10 Outubr 1964, Dutt bhaddean ghetolea ghorant khattir melolo sampoddlo jem Mumboint  Pedder Road bhagant aslem. To sorea vangdda nhidpacheo gulleo mixronn kortalo oxem sangpant ieta.. Tachem moronn ghoddiek atmghat zanv ieta vo chodd gulleo ghevpachi ek obsoegachi ghoddnni. To ghoddiek tachea tisrea atmghatacho proiotn zanv ieta..<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://in.rediff.com/movies/2004/oct/08spec1.htm|title='Guru Dutt attempted suicide thrice' – Rediff.com movies|date=8 October 2004|publisher=In.rediff.com|access-date=3 September 2016}}</ref>

Dutta-cho put, Arun Dutt, haka tem mornn obsoegan zalam mhonn dislam. Dusrea disa Mala Sinha nottie ani Raj Kapoor kolakara lagim tachea Baharen Phir Bhi Aayengi, filma vixim tacher bhasabhas korunk rongit filma kaddpa vixim Dutta-k tharavik apovnnim aslim.Tachea pormonnem, "Mhojea bapaik nhidpachi pidda asli ani to gulleo heram bhaxen ghetalo. Tea disa to soro pielolo ani tannem odik gulleo ghetleo jea vorvim taka mornn ievnk pavlem.Tem chodd soro ani chodd nhidpacheo gulleo ghevop, ek jiv ghevpi zavnk pavlem.."<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/2004/oct/15dutt.htm|title='I miss my father terribly'|last=Ashraf, Syed Firdaus|date=15 October 2004|website=Rediff.com|access-date=5 July 2010}}</ref>

Mornnachea vellar, Dutt her don prokolpamni gunthlolo aslo - Picnic zantunt Sadhana notti, ani digdorspi K. Asifachem mhakaveo, Love and God. Picnic ordemkhurem urlem ani Love and God don doskam uprant sador korpant ailem zantunt Sanjeev Kumaran mukhel patracho Dutta-cho zago ghetlo.

Kaagaz Ke Phool DVDche  odik manddavollint, ek tin bhaganchi Channel 4 Dutt-achea jivit ani vavracher ek mhaitipott asa zachem nanv In Search of Guru Dutt 

Duttacher 10 Outubr 2011 vorsa,ek Doordarshan mhaitipott vitravpant ailo.

== Khasgi jivit[sudar] ==
1953 vorsa , Dutt, Geeta Roy Chaudhary, uprant Geeta Dutt kodde logn zalo, ji ek famad fattbhuinchi gavpi asli. Tanchi soirik tin vorsam adim zaloli ani tankam kuttumbachi oddchonn logn zavpa vixim bhogchi poddli zancho hea logna vixim virodh aslo. Tankam tin bhurgim aslim, Tarun, Arun ani Nina, jim Duttacho bhavr Atma Ram ani Geeta Duttacho bhav Mukul Roychea ghorabeant vaddlim jen’na tanche avoibapui somple.[14].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rediff.com/movies/report/guru-dutts-son-passes-away/20140728.htm|title=Guru Dutt's son passes away|date=28 July 2014|website=Rediff.com movies|access-date=5 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/mumbai/guru-dutts-son-arun-passes-away/article6257465.ece|title=Guru Dutt’s son Arun passes away|date=28 July 2014|website=The Hindu|access-date=5 April 2016}}</ref>

Duttachem lognachem jivit khuxalkaiechem naslem. Tacho bhava  Atmaram-a pormonnem to ek " kama vixim koddok xisticho aslo, punn khasgi jivitant to oxisticho aslo" [17] To chodd sigretti voddttalo ani bhorpur soro pietalo ani vellachem taka bhan naslem.. Dutt-achi Waheeda Rehman nottie kodde ixttagot tanchea lognacher add ienvk pavli Mornnachea vellar, to Geeta pasun kuxin sorlolo ani ekloch jietalo. Geeta Dutt 1972  vorsa 41vorsanche piraier sompli  kiteak soro khub pion tichem figd, bigoddlolem.

== Daiz[sudar] ==
