Tachea film prokolpachea vevhara bodol zorui add ulovpant ieta, Duttan choddxim iesvont filma prostut kelim.[18]Vorsam pottim tachea vepari soim tachea prokolpachim tachea sorjonxil havesak sath dinvk pavlim nant.Filma zoxim C.I.D., Baazi, Pyaasa, Kaagaz Ke Phool, Chaudhvin Ka Chand ani Sahib Bibi Aur Ghulam, him Hindi sinemant poilim koxim aslim.Ekuch film jem Duttak ek chodd komavpant opiesi aslem tem Kaagaz Ke Phool,jem atam ek somprodaiechem abhzat asa. To.1.7 milhanv rupia tea filmant luskon zalo, tea kallar hi rokom chodd asli ji tannem fuddlea Chaudhvin Ka Chand filmant bhorun kaddli,. Tannem aplea pongddacher vo vitorokancher  dovorlolo bhorvonso ken’nach soddunk na. Ek favtti prokolp somplo mhonnttoch, to novean suru kortalo- ani taka adlea prokolpachem vepari iesachem poddun vochunk naslem.To Raj Kapoor, Mehboob Khan ani Bimal Roy, sangata thoddea Bharoti film digdorspeam modlo eklo zannem kola ani vepari iesacho tall mell modlea 1950 ani modlea1960 modem zomoilo.

''Pyaasa hem film sogllea vorsam modem xemborantlem ek  oxi Time magazine hannem tachi tulna kelea.[1]  2002 vorsa Sight & Sound ttikekar ani digdorspeanchea venchnnukent, tachim don filma, Pyaasa ani Kaagaz Ke Phool, poilea 160 boreantlea filma modem zavn asat.[2] Teach 2002 vorsa Sight & Sound hachea venchnnukent sogllea vorsantlea boreantlea digdorspeam modem Dutt-ak #73  ankddo dila, jea vorvim taka atthvo vhodd zago Asiai filmtoiar korpeam  modem tea venchnnukent favo zala''.<ref name="Lee">{{Cite web|url=http://www.asianamericanfilm.com/archives/000026.html|title=A Slanted Canon|last=Lee, Kevin|date=5 September 2002|publisher=Asian American Film Commentary|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/684ysTg3l?url=http://www.asianamericanfilm.com/archives/000026.html|archive-date=31 May 2012|dead-url=yes|access-date=24 April 2009}}</ref>

